  "prompt": "Which Harry Potter character was worst portrayed in the movies?",
  "response": "Opinions on character portrayals in the Harry Potter movies can vary widely among fans. However, one character often mentioned as being underwhelming or poorly portrayed in comparison to the books is Ginny Weasley. Many fans feel that her character was not given enough depth and development in the films, especially considering her significant role in the source material.\n\nAnother character frequently discussed is Peeves the Poltergeist, who was omitted entirely from the film adaptations. Some fans feel that his absence detracts from the overall atmosphere of Hogwarts.\n\nUltimately, which character was the \"worst portrayed\" can be subjective and depends on individual perspectives and attachment to the characters from the books.",
